examples.en: I was deeply influenced by my parents.
Who influenced her to do that?
It's a given that television viewers are influenced by advertising, even consciously or subconsciously.
The price of oil has influenced the price of industrial goods.
What influenced you to take up nursing?
The artist's work influenced the young painter.
Marx was strongly influenced by the historian Niebuhr.
Allison's vocal style is influenced by country and blues music.
All of the authors named above were influenced by his work.
More factors influenced her decision than she cares to admit.
Was his decision influenced by any illegal financial inducements?
They conspired to replace the leader with someone more easily influenced.
The House was influenced in its decision by the gravity of the financial crisis.
She claims that her decision to resign was not influenced by her personal problems.
A person's behavior can be influenced by urges that exist only in the subconscious.
They argued that the presence of TV cameras at the trial influenced the behavior of attorneys, witnesses, and jurors.
Our decision to build the museum in Hartlepool was influenced by the fact that there were no national museums in the North East.
